   - **Add/Edit modal form** with title, topic, skill, tags, content, and draft toggle
   - **Autosave**: `content` auto-saves as a draft to IndexedDB with 1.5s debounce — creates the note automatically if it doesn't exist yet (with `isDraft: true`); `title` also autosaves when editing
   - **Validation**: title is required
   - **Actions**: favorite toggle, draft/publish toggle, delete with toast

